			<SecondaryPreamble>
				<EnactingText>
					<Para>
						<Text>The Department for Regional Development<FootnoteRef Ref="f00001"/> makes the following Regulations in exercise of the powers conferred by Article 28(2) of the Road Traffic Regulation (Northern Ireland) Order 1997<FootnoteRef Ref="f00002"/> and now vested in it<FootnoteRef Ref="f00003"/>:</Text>
